{"tid":635533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯「殺無赦」言論　經過7個月調查後 警方不檢控 案件已完成調查","createTime":"2018-04-20T07:57:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T13:14:42.000Z","uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"75c470c5c38e2f21ce4204f3c658989f52adfd5a","tid":635533,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T07:57:35.000Z","msg":"立法會議員何君堯去年9月，在金鐘的一個集會上，提到有關「殺無赦」的言論，列作「求警調查」案件。警方說，經過7個月調查後，沒有足夠證據對任何人提出檢控，案件已完成調查。 去年9月17日，何君堯在添馬公園發起集會，以「反港獨、反冷血、反偽學」為主題，批評佔中發起人、港大法律學系副教授戴耀廷，指對方是散播「港獨」思潮的罪魁禍首，要求港大開除他。 <br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1392257-20180420.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1392257-20180420.htm&d=7BieEHDRrS%2FIJH8FDuFIagdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=7f38b60f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1392257-20180420.htm&h=cd609a7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1392257-20180420.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2ca1b61a9b320af20ae3e66fd7058d9a69c8570c","tid":635533,"uid":188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T07:58:03.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"758d0e6a2315cb97efcc845c5ca22448fd2fca67","tid":635533,"uid":188,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T07:58:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/20/155849_f9d5e9a39d2e60026822adf74d5bc64b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F20%2F155849_f9d5e9a39d2e60026822adf74d5bc64b.jpg&h=18dde9fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a3643c7c5a7129400de0be3ec4d3cd0131a7e3d","tid":635533,"uid":28446,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T08:00:35.000Z","msg":"極醜惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\"